### [choco://intel-killer-performance-suite](choco://intel-killer-performance-suite/s=https://nuts.bcurran3.org/nuget/chocolatey/)
To use choco:// protocol URLs, install [choco:// Protocol support ](https://nuts.bcurran3.org/feeds/chocolatey/choco-protocol-support/versions)


---

This download installs Wi-Fi, Ethernet drivers and Killer Software for the Intel® Killer™ products.
 

